PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?production ?character WHERE {
  ?production wdt:P161 wd:Q207598 ; p:P161 ?statement .
  ?statement pq:P453 ?character .
}

PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?senator WHERE {
  VALUES ?senator {
    wd:Q453893 wd:Q359888
  }
  ?senator p:P39 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P39 wd:Q4416090 .
  ?statement pq:P580 ?start .
  ?statement pq:P582 ?end .
  FILTER ( ?start <= "2013-12-31" ^^ xsd:date && ?end >= "2013-01-01" ^^ xsd:date )
}

PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?actress WHERE {
  wd:Q3577037 p:P161 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P161 ?actress ; pq:P453 wd:Q3036775 .
}

PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?year ?winner WHERE {
  ?win wdt:P31 wd:Q265538 .
  ?win wdt:P585 "1995-01-01T00:00:00Z" ^^ xsd:dateTime .
  ?win wdt:P1346 ?winner .
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?college WHERE {
  wd:Q213346 wdt:P69 ?college .
  ?college wdt:P31 ?type .
  FILTER ( ?type = wd:Q3918 || ?type = wd:Q189004 || ?type = wd:Q110225820 || ?type = wd:Q23002054 )
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?givenName ?familyName WHERE {
  wd:Q312581 wdt:P735 ?givenName .
  wd:Q312581 wdt:P734 ?familyName .
  FILTER ( ?givenName = wd:Q2958359 )
}

PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?coach WHERE {
  wd:Q330120 p:P286 ?stmt .
  ?stmt ps:P286 ?coach .
  ?stmt pq:P580 ?startTime .
  ?stmt pq:P582 ?endTime .
  FILTER ( ?startTime <= "2013-01-01T00:00:00Z" ^^ xsd:dateTime && "2013-01-01T00:00:00Z" ^^ xsd:dateTime <= ?endTime )
}

PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?voiceActor ?startDate WHERE {
  wd:Q908772 p:P725 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P725 ?voiceActor ; pq:P580 ?startDate .
}
ORDER BY ASC ( ?startDate )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?location ?locationLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q714185 wdt:P20 ?location .
  ?location rdfs:label ?locationLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?locationLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>

SELECT ?start ?end WHERE {
  wd:Q91 p:P39 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P39 wd:Q11696 .
  ?statement pq:P580 ?start .
  ?statement pq:P582 ?end
}

PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?actor WHERE {

  ?statement p:P161 ?actorStatement .

PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?startDate WHERE {
  wd:Q33866 p:P39 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P39 wd:Q11696 .
  ?statement pq:P580 ?startDate .
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?highSchool ?highSchoolLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q182658 wdt:P69 ?highSchool .
  ?highSchool rdfs:label ?highSchoolLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?highSchoolLabel ) = "en" ) FILTER ( CONTAINS( ?highSchoolLabel , "High School" ) )
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?superBowl ?year WHERE {
  ?superBowl wdt:P31 wd:Q32096 .
  ?superBowl wdt:P1346 wd:Q276539 .
  ?superBowl wdt:P585 ?year .
}

PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
ASK WHERE {
  wd:Q9640 p:P39 ?vicePresidentStatement .
  ?vicePresidentStatement ps:P39 wd:Q11699 ; pq:P580 ?start ; pq:P582 ?end .
  FILTER ( ?start <= "1963-11-22" ^^ xsd:date && ?end >= "1961-01-20" ^^ xsd:date )
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?country WHERE {
  wd:Q9441 wdt:P19 ?placeOfBirth .
  ?placeOfBirth wdt:P131 * ?country .
  ?country wdt:P31 wd:Q6256 .
}

PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?team ?startDate WHERE {
  wd:Q296403 p:P54 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P54 ?team .
  ?statement pq:P580 ?startDate .
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?startDate )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?primeMinister ?primeMinisterLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q29 p:P6 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P6 ?primeMinister ; pq:P580 ?startDate ; pq:P582 ?endDate .
  FILTER ( ?startDate <= "2011-12-31" ^^ xsd:dateTime && ?endDate >= "2011-01-01" ^^ xsd:dateTime ) OPTIONAL {
    ?primeMinister rdfs:label ?primeMinisterLabel .
    FILTER ( LANG( ?primeMinisterLabel ) = "en" )
  }
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>

SELECT ?player ?playerLabel WHERE {
  ?player wdt:P647 wd:Q162990 .
  ?player rdfs:label ?playerLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?playerLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
